With Sister Location almost here I was getting super antsy, so Jason found me some Sister Location fan games to tide me over until the big day - that was, until we found Scott's official upload and statement of release for Sister Location: MA. That's Right, Sister Location: MA Has Been Uploaded by Scott! HYPE!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
